  "summary": "Re-tested 4 assertions after fix commit 'Fix LiveView flash bug: put live_session routes through browser pipeline'. All 4 assertions now pass: VAL-AUTH-003 (guests blocked from /dashboard), VAL-AUTH-005 (admin can access /admin), VAL-AUTH-006 (non-admin denied from /admin), VAL-CROSS-001 (first-visit auth partitioning consistent). The LiveView flash bug has been resolved."
